sources.description:
After a chance encounter in the Montana wilderness, family man Bill Burdick and failed drug dealer Devin Fowler form an unlikely bond, and soon find themselves concocting an unorthodox scheme to resolve their financial debts. But as their plan starts to unravel, their dire circumstances and toxic chemistry give way to greed, violence, and far-reaching psychological trauma.

2021.  Stars: Joe Basso, Robert Shupe, Mabel Maultsby
